Title: Xenium_small
Description: 10x Genomics Xenium mock .h5 count matrix file and cells.csv.gz file downsized from the human breast cancer  replicate 1 in Janesick et al. (2023).

Title: CosMx_small
Description: NanoString CosMx mock .csv count matrix file and .csv coordinates file downsized from the human NSCLC data (patient 9, slice 1). This dataset was previously released by NanoString on their website.

Title: MERSCOPE_small
Description: Vizgen MERSCOPE mock .csv count matrix file and .csv coordinates file downsized from the human ovarian (patient 2, sample 1). This dataset was previously released by Vizgen on their website.

Title: STARmapPLUS_small
Description: STARmap PLUS mock .csv count matrix file and .csv coordinates file downsized from the mouse brain (well 05), including annotations for cell type and tissue regions by Shi et al. (2023).

Title: seqFISH_small
Description: Spatial Genomics seqFISH human unknown dataset obtained from Github issue #3 by Github user methornton.
